            <h3>Planned Modules & Features</h3>
            <p>Our software is being built with a modular approach, allowing us to add powerful features over time. Here are some key modules we have planned:</p>
            <ul class="mt-4">
                <li>
                    <strong>Basic Invoicing:</strong> Create and manage professional invoices with ease. Add line items, quantities, rates, and calculate totals automatically.
                </li>
                <li>
                    <strong>Client Address Book:</strong> A centralized place to store all your client contact and billing information. Autofill client details on invoices for speed.
                </li>
                <li>
                    <strong>Basic Inventory:</strong> Manage a list of your products or services. Easily add inventory items to invoices with pre-filled descriptions and prices. Helps track what you're selling.
                </li>
                <li>
                    <strong>Payment Tracking:</strong> Mark invoices as paid (full or partial), track payment dates, and see who owes you money at a glance.
                </li>
                 <li>
                    <strong>Online Payment Integration:</strong> Connect with popular payment gateways ([Specify examples like Stripe, PayPal]) to allow your clients to pay you directly online, getting you paid faster.
                </li>
                 <li>
                    <strong>Recurring Invoices & Subscriptions:</strong> Set up invoices that are automatically generated and sent to repeat clients on a schedule (weekly, monthly, annually). Perfect for retainer services.
                </li>
                 <li>
                    <strong>Reporting & Analytics:</strong> Get valuable insights into your sales, track outstanding payments, view client purchase history, and generate reports to understand your business performance.
                </li>
                 <li>
                    <strong>Tax Management:</strong> Configure different tax rates and apply them accurately to your invoices. Simplify tax calculations and reporting.
                </li>
                 <li>
                    <strong>Estimates & Quotes:</strong> Create and send professional estimates or quotes to potential clients. Easily convert an accepted estimate into a ready-to-send invoice.
                </li>
                 <li>
                    <strong>Automated Reminders:</strong> Set up the software to automatically send polite payment reminders to clients for upcoming or overdue invoices, saving you manual effort.
                </li>
                 <li>
                    <strong>Customizable Templates:</strong> Personalize the look of your invoices with your own logo, colors, and layout options to maintain brand consistency.
                </li>
                 <li>
                    <strong>User Roles & Permissions:</strong> (For teams) Allow multiple users with different access levels to collaborate securely.
                </li>
                 <li>
                    <strong>Attachments:</strong> Ability to attach relevant files (like contracts, project scopes, or receipts) directly to invoices or client records.
                </li>
            </ul>
